o, please!"],[6319,6413,"Let me go!"],[6419,6606,"That's, that's my baby girl!"]],"58":[[744,820,"Where's Dad?"],[820,914,"Is he not back yet?"],[947,1024,"What about Angelica?"],[1024,1137,"None of them are home yet."],[1314,1408,"Well, I checked at school,"],[1408,1494,"and she wasn't there."],[1558,1628,"It must've been wrong,"],[1628,1711,"it wasn't Angie."],[1878,1978,"And I got this,"],[2058,2202,"this, this feeling like"],[2202,2318,"something already happened."],[2372,2492,"Something I can't fix."],[2545,2719,"Maybe you just need to eat something."],[3360,3406,"Dad."],[3466,3660,"Jeez, how much did he drink?"],[3747,3857,"Hey, Dad, what, what happened?"],[3857,3973,"You haven't had a drink in years."],[4010,4157,"I'm sorry."],[4210,4444,"I'm so sorry."],[4444,4564,"Angelica,"],[4597,4841,"I'm a terrible father."],[5051,5148,"What are you talking about?"],[5168,5338,"I failed, Stella."],[5338,5508,"I'm a coward."],[5508,5795,"I, I couldn't protect our daughter."],[5832,5965,"It was all my fault."],[5969,6089,"Dad, what is going on?"],[6089,6222,"Where's, where's Angelica?"],[6493,6763,"Angelica is gone."],[7067,7237,"She's dead."],[7464,7547,"What?"]],"59":[[26,76,"What?"],[156,250,"What? No, no."],[250,457,"She, she ran away, she's fine."],[483,643,"Chris, calm down."],[643,807,"Your, your dad is clearly wasted."],[807,924,"He, he doesn't know what he's saying."],[924,1037,"Angelica is fine."],[1047,1111,"Where is she?"],[1111,1197,"Where's Angelica?"],[1331,1394,"Here."],[1574,1841,"She's right here."],[2202,2322,"I'm sick, Chris."],[2382,2532,"Your little sister is dying."],[2669,2799,"You must be so happy now."],[2859,2969,"Don't worry, Christopher."],[3046,3169,"I'll never bother you again."],[3249,3370,"There's something wrong with Angie!"],[3523,3656,"She has cancer!"],[4090,4237,"Body donation acknowledgment?"],[4531,4674,"No, no, Angelica,"],[4674,4774,"Angelica is dead?"],[4774,4888,"No, no, no!"],[4888,4951,"This isn't real!"],[4951,5045,"And she j