essing with me."],[663,846,"Hm? Angelica is just mad,"],[846,1001,"and that's why she's pulling this prank."],[1026,1146,"Face it, Christopher."],[1146,1238,"She's gone."],[1338,1443,"The cancer took her."],[1897,1976,"Angie."],[2039,2164,"It's not you in there."],[2193,2318,"Alright, tell me it's not you."],[2510,2590,"Let her rest."],[2627,2698,"I brought you here,"],[2698,2777,"so you can learn to live"],[2777,2861,"with what you did."],[2919,3082,"Every ounce of pain she felt,"],[3103,3249,"I'm gonna make sure you feel it too."],[3328,3390,"Chris!"],[3803,3974,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[4024,4204,"Get away from Aunt Stella's grave!"],[4237,4391,"You are such a punk,"],[4391,4508,"just like Angelica!"],[4650,4733,"Chris!"],[4733,4875,"Did you just push me?"],[4875,5100,"No one talks about my sister like that."]],"69":[[13,193,"What's wrong with you today, Chris?"],[230,340,"Didn't you say that I'm"],[360,490,"your only sister?"],[670,874,"Angie is my only sister."],[917,957,"Alright?"],[957,1121,"Always has been, and always will be."],[1121,1247,"But Chris, I..."],[1338,1481,"Look, I even came here"],[1481,1601,"to visit Aunt Stella,"],[1601,1741,"Angelica didn't even remember"],[1741,1871,"her death anniversary."],[2362,2552,"Angelica!"],[2552,2866,"My baby girl, I'm sorry!"],[2866,3126,"I was a terrible father,"],[3126,3336,"and I failed you and your mom."],[3730,3880,"I'll come"],[3880,4030,"see you soon."],[4070,4210,"Angelica's really dead?"],[4297,4357,"Finally."],[4404,4454,"That means"],[4454,4581,"Christopher's mine now."],[4601,4694,"Oh my God,"],[4694,4914,"Angelica's really gone?"],[4914,4998,"That's her grave?"],[5045,5118,"Chris,"],[5158,5335,"I know this must be so hard for you."],[5335,5588,"But it's okay, I'm still here."],[5588,5749,"And I'm not going anywhere."],[5765,5892,"You make me sick."],[6122,6252,"Did you just hit me?"],[6252,6332,"Damn right I did."],[6332,6509,"I wanted to do that for years."],[6683,6840,"And that one was for Angelica."]],"70":[[56,240,"Chris, she's insane!"],[240,330,"Help me!"],[390,433,"Raven-"],[433,547,"You're just gonna defend her?"],[860,1001,"You know what this bitch has done?"],[1074,1204,"She broke your mom's necklace."],[1204,1327,"She ruined the portraits."],[1327,1438,"It was all her!"],[1688,1735,"What?"],[1818,1885,"Madison,"],[1965,2098,"please tell me she's lying."],[2122,2208,"Don't listen to her."],[2222,2322,"She and Angie"],[2322,2479,"were always ganging up on me."],[2562,2609,"Ah."],[2866,2966,"And that's for what happened"],[2966,3049,"in the locker room."],[3049,3123,"You made her worse."],[3123,3256,"You beat her until she puked blood,"],[3256,3380,"and now you pay."],[3433,3476,"I didn't."],[3553,3663,"Chris, I swear,"],[3663,3807,"I would never do something like that!"],[3807,3953,"You have to believe me."],[3983,4114,"Madison is lying!"],[4461,4554,"She was the one"],[4554,4784,"bullying Angelica for years."],[4784,4928,"I can testify to that."]],"71":[[3,110,"Angelica is gone,"],[146,253,"and after today,"],[253,437,"I am done working for this family."],[473,587,"But before I go,"],[613,784,"I'm setting the record straight."],[784,994,"Shut up, you old hag."],[994,1104,"No, you shut up!"],[1351,1401,"Fiona,"],[1474,1558,"thank you for coming."],[1558,1695,"Calling you was the right move."],[1695,1821,"Angelica died"],[1821,1978,"bearing the pain she didn't deserve."],[2008,2102,"And look, I might have just"],[2102,2222,"been a housekeeper,"],[2285,2392,"but I loved that girl,"],[2425,2529,"like she was mine."],[2562,2625,"It was her."],[2665,2886,"She was the one who bullied Angelica."],[2922,3099,"She, she set her up,"],[3163,3329,"turned her own brother against her,"],[3396,3493,"and I saw her"],[3520,3723,"breaking Mrs. Ray's necklace"],[3723,3860,"with my own eyes."],[3927,3967,"At first,"],[3967,4104,"I thought it was just an argument."],[4210,4334,"I figured they would make up."],[4467,4521,"I didn't think"],[4521,4694,"she was gonna pin it on Angelica."],[4894,4988,"Poor Angelica."],[5191,5305,"She would have never,"],[5321,5545,"never damaged her mother's necklace."],[5578,5702,"She was innocent."],[5745,5825,"It was you."]],"72":[[10,126,"And that portrait?"],[577,657,"That's weird."],[687,807,"Where are the scissors?"],[1327,1451,"Oh, not again!"],[1571,1695,"You didn't believe your own sister,"],[1695,1765,"did you?"],[1838,1971,"You sided with a bully."],[2092,2202,"Don't bother, Fiona."],[2312,2392,"You can't win against someone"],[2392,2492,"who's already picked a side."],[2519,2625,"No matter what I do,"],[2686,2826,"you'll always defend her."],[2826,2919,"I get it now."],[2979,3039,"You know,"],[3039,3193,"if hating me makes it easier for you,"],[3193,3289,"then go ahead."],[3323,3526,"It's all my fault!"],[4017,4114,"I don't wanna see you again."],[4180,4230,"Ever!"],[4304,4404,"So get out."],[4451,4607,"Get the fuck out!"],[4671,4758,"It was all my fault."],[4948,5031,"Madison,"],[5121,5238,"you're gonna regret it."]],"73":[[13,130,"Angelica was the one that brought you"],[130,256,"into the house, huh?"],[313,467,"And this is how you repaid her?"],[510,660,"No, Chris, please!"],[684,944,"I just lost it for a second, okay?"],[967,1087,"You know what I've been through."],[1151,1334,"I lost both of my parents,"],[1334,1591,"and I was just afraid of losing you too."],[1735,1928,"Hey, remember who cooked"],[1928,2105,"Uncle Martin's birthday cake,"],[2105,2192,"and who walked together"],[2192,2328,"to school every day,"],[2369,2569,"and who cheered you on at every game?"],[2645,2836,"You are all I have left."],[2969,3136,"I loved you like a brother."],[3169,3243,"And please,"],[3319,3390,"don't hate me."],[3463,3546,"Forgive me."],[3777,3827,"Ah!"],[3857,3927,"My leg!"],[3980,4034,"My leg!"],[4034,4060,"I..."],[4130,4244,"I'm the cheer captain."],[4244,4391,"I can't lose my leg!"],[4391,4494,"Wow, yeah, that hurts."],[4494,4631,"Imagine how she felt, huh?"],[4657,4824,"Now get out of my house!"],[4861,4991,"Alright, I don't wanna see you again!"],[5035,5185,"Okay, I'll leave."],[5185,5301,"Just don't hate me."],[5331,5458,"You think this is over?"],[5458,5518,"Huh?"],[5518,5645,"Get away from me!"],[5645,5785,"You moved into the Ray's house,"],[5785,5855,"and after,"],[5855,6012,"Angelica was assaulted"],[6012,6092,"after school."],[6092,6176,"You expect me to believe"],[6176,6282,"that's just a coincidence?"],[6282,6336,"I, I don't know"],[6336,6423,"what you're talking about."],[6423,6519,"I have to go."]],"74":[[180,357,"So it was you, huh?"],[413,563,"You were the one that sent the people?"],[597,677,"I didn't!"],[727,827,"Christopher. - Hm?"],[847,957,"I, I didn't. - Christopher."],[957,1077,"I can't breathe. - Stop!"],[1077,1171,"You're killing her!"],[1631,1805,"It wasn't me."],[1895,2138,"Yeah, I was jealous of Angie, okay?"],[2182,2325,"But I would never do something"],[2325,2409,"that messed up."],[2409,2502,"Believe me."],[2502,2589,"Still lying?"],[2619,2826,"We have the entire truth on camera."],[2826,2899,"What camera?"],[2986,3079,"You don't know, huh?"],[3163,3263,"We installed a camera"],[3263,3343,"in the living room,"],[3426,3610,"it caught everything."],[3680,3730,"What?"],[3793,3837,"How?"],[3933,4044,"No, no, don't watch it!"],[4044,4144,"Chris, no, don't!"]],"75":[[600,675,"That night,"],[763,955,"I was the one who sent the guys"],[1026,1238,"to teach you a lesson."],[1297,1393,"How'd it feel?"],[1710,1843,"How could you?"],[1893,1985,"I've seen enough."],[2052,2139,"You fucking bitch."],[2139,2277,"No, no, please!"],[2369,2477,"Apologize to Angelica now."],[2790,2923,"Chris, I was wrong!"],[3044,3144,"I'm sorry, I,"],[3144,3257,"I'm so sorry."],[3257,3461,"Are you fucking kidding me?"],[3645,3807,"So, you really think I loved you?"],[3887,3987,"No, I was just,"],[3987,4095,"I was just pretending to"],[4095,4220,"piss off Angelica."],[4220,4262,"No."],[4320,4404,"You're lying."],[4466,4567,"You love me!"],[4617,4863,"Look, the only person I ever cared for"],[4950,5046,"was Angie."],[5046,5096,"No."],[5096,5155,"You go to hell."],[5184,5334,"No!"]],"76":[[140,243,"No, no, no."],[243,363,"Please, please!"],[407,603,"No, please, please!"],[603,660,"No."],[787,877,"Thank you, Fiona."],[934,994,"Without that video,"],[994,1147,"Madison would've never been caught."],[1207,1331,"That's the least I could do"],[1331,1438,"for that poor girl."],[1498,1644,"Now that Madison's gone,"],[1644,1735,"we have a better chance"],[1735,1861,"at tracking down the other two."],[1915,1968,"Yeah."],[2108,2162,"We did it."],[3076,3116,"Here."],[3183,3303,"Angelica wanted you to have this."],[3303,3443,"She said it before she died."],[4007,4104,"Tell me, when uh,"],[4240,4401,"when Angie left, was she in pain?"],[4507,4604,"Her body was."],[4664,4724,"Towards the end,"],[4724,4844,"she could barely breathe."],[5001,5078,"But inside,"],[5078,5201,"she wasn't hurting anymore."],[5388,5598,"She said she got to do what she wanted."],[5772,5822,"I took her"],[5822,5912,"somewhere beautiful,"],[5912,6116,"and she said she saw her mom."]],"77":[[290,457,"I know they're together now,"],[457,550,"and they're happy."],[663,757,"I should go."],[790,860,"She always said"],[860,977,"she wanted to see the world,"],[977,1154,"and I'm gonna go see it for her."],[2198,2275,"Dear Chris,"],[2335,2462,"by the time you read this,"],[2472,2579,"I'll probably be gone."],[3186,3323,"I fixed Mom's necklace."],[3603,3710,"It's yours now."],[3940,4017,"You said you wanted me"],[4017,4114,"out of your life,"],[4154,4270,"so I'm making it happen."],[4307,4391,"Bye, Chris."],[4541,4594,"Bye, Dad."],[4864,4984,"I just hope, somehow,"],[5065,5201,"that this makes you happy."]],"78":[[76,180,"And under the stars,"],[180,270,"they promised"],[270,417,"they'd be together forever."],[790,857,"Angie, you really"],[857,977,"made me work for that."],[1057,1211,"It took me a while to finish that book,"],[1211,1351,"but hey, at least I"],[1351,1488,"got to keep you company."],[1578,1765,"Oh, and Zack wanted to come."],[1831,1975,"Like I'd bring that idiot."],[2042,2105,"No way."],[2335,2422,"Look at this."],[3183,3289,"I finally graduated."],[3553,3677,"Just like you always said I would."],[3797,3893,"It was brutal though."],[3893,4030,"Like, no parties."],[4070,4200,"Just me in the library."],[4254,4371,"My friends all thought"],[4371,4531,"I'd completely lost it."],[4794,4971,"Sorry, I promised I wouldn't cry."],[5175,5432,"It, it's probably the wind or something."],[5618,5699,"You probably saw your mom"],[5699,5772,"up there, right?"],[6326,6423,"Raven, don't cry."],[6486,6643,"You're the tough one, remember?"]],"79":[[210,246,"Yeah,"],[330,457,"tough girls don't cry."],[563,603,"Right?"],[663,734,"Those, uh,"],[734,890,"those two assholes that hurt you,"],[890,1021,"they were finally caught."],[1101,1214,"They ended up in"],[1214,1421,"one of the worst prisons out there."],[1421,1631,"And they got beaten up so bad"],[1631,1791,"that they'll never walk right again."],[1821,1958,"It didn't last long after that."],[2005,2125,"And, uh, as for Madison"],[2125,2432,"that demon is rotting in prison,"],[2432,2525,"for the rest of her life."],[2525,2682,"I've got a few friends inside"],[2682,2782,"making sure she gets"],[2782,2896,"what she deserves."],[3076,3213,"She's paying for every damn thing"],[3213,3309,"she did to you."],[3363,3446,"You know you, you showed up"],[3446,3583,"in my dream the other night,"],[3583,3737,"and asked about your dad."],[3813,3907,"And,"],[4024,4204,"well, he could not handle the guilt"],[4204,4294,"of losing you,"],[4294,4494,"he started drinking heavily."],[4537,4728,"He lost his medical license."],[4728,4931,"His body gave out not long after."],[4931,5038,"I mean, Christopher"],[5038,5171,"handled the funeral."],[5248,5425,"And he buried him,"],[5425,5658,"but not next to you and Stella."],[5658,5752,"If he had, I swear,"],[5752,5905,"I would've beat the crap out of him."],[5939,6132,"And, uh, as for Christopher,"],[6132,6329,"he dropped out of school, disappeared."],[6443,6593,"No one knows where he went."]],"80":[[258,308,"Angie..."],[367,425,"loves candy."],[425,487,"loves candy."],[592,709,"I got her the biggest one,"],[709,796,"you're not gonna take it."],[796,892,"It's hers."],[1109,1180,"Forget him."],[1259,1305,"Let's go."],[1347,1443,"Bro's lost his mind."],[2857,2907,"Her favorite."]],"81":[[1311,1388,"Eat this."],[1411,1488,"It's sweet."],[3770,3810,"Chris,"],[3867,3943,"is it sweet?"],[4157,4200,"Yeah."],[4240,4354,"Yeah, it is really good."],[4414,4467,"Here, have it."],[4467,4551,"It's all yours."],[4684,4788,"I forgive you, Chris."],[4808,4931,"I'll always love you."],[5592,5689,"Angie, I'm coming."],[5889,5995,"We'll be a real family."],[6863,6903,"What the..."],[7000,7143,"I'm seven?"]],"82":[[797,834,"What the..."],[930,1084,"I'm seven?"],[1177,1254,"So, I think we're gonna need-"],[1254,1431,"Daddy, it hurts! - a CT scan."],[1431,1561,"Yeah, and um..."],[1908,2002,"Stop right there,"],[2002,2098,"Martin Ray!"],[2182,2252,"Hold on one second."],[2402,2509,"Chris, what did you just call me?"],[2525,2686,"You're a terrible dad!"],[2756,2969,"It's not Angie's fault Mom died."],[3003,3209,"Wake up and be there for her."],[3336,3570,"Are you really my son?"],[3590,3690,"You bet I am."],[3690,3903,"Now pick her up and give her a hug!"],[4664,4861,"I'm sorry, Angie."],[5015,5135,"Your brother's right."],[5135,5311,"I have been running away."],[5398,5608,"You look so much like your mom."],[5658,5809,"That is no excuse."],[5929,6016,"From now on,"],[6099,6212,"I'll be there for you."],[6246,6489,"Angie, I'll do better this time."],[6489,6589,"I'm not letting"],[6589,6726,"anything happen to you."],[6753,6960,"I'll protect you no matter what."],[6980,7127,"Thank you, Daddy."],[7360,7464,"I love you, Chris."],[7464,7664,"You're the best big brother ever."],[7734,7807,"Angie,"],[7894,7977,"this time,"],[7997,8101,"I'll make sure you're treated"],[8101,8181,"like the princess"],[8181,8314,"you've always deserved to be."],[8385,8461,"I promise."]]}